<section><title>Purpose</title><indexterm>programming interface calls<indexterm>ParsGetSeg</indexterm></indexterm><indexterm>ParsGetSeg</indexterm><indexterm>parser API<indexterm>ParsGetSeg</indexterm></indexterm>
<p><i>ParsGetSeg</i> gets a segment from the segmented
file loaded into memory.</p>
<p>If the segment in Unicode format, use <xref href="mut_ParsGetSegW.dita#mut_ParsGetSegW"/>.</p>
</section>
